<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #4a90e2;
      --secondary-color: #5c6bc0;
      --text-color: #333;
      --light-text: #666;
      --border-color: #eaeaea;
      --code-bg: #f5f7f9;
      --blockquote-bg: #f9f9f9;
      --blockquote-border: #e0e0e0;
      --header-bg: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-color);
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    
    .header {
      background: var(--header-bg);
      color: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .header p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 0 2rem 2rem;
    }
    
    h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
      margin-top: 1.5em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75em;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.25;
      color: var(--text-color);
    }
    
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 0.3em; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 0.3em; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    h4 { font-size: 1rem; }
    
    p, ul, ol {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }
    
    a {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    code {
      font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;
      background-color: var(--code-bg);
      padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
    
    pre {
      background-color: var(--code-bg);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 1em;
      overflow: auto;
      margin: 1em 0;
    }
    
    pre code {
      background-color: transparent;
      padding: 0;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      line-height: 1.5;
      display: block;
    }
    
    blockquote {
      margin: 1em 0;
      padding: 0.5em 1em;
      color: var(--light-text);
      background-color: var(--blockquote-bg);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--blockquote-border);
    }
    
    blockquote p {
      margin: 0.5em 0;
    }
    
    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 1em auto;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    
    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 1em 0;
    }
    
    table th, table td {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      padding: 0.5em 1em;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    table th {
      background-color: var(--code-bg);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    hr {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: var(--border-color);
      border: none;
      margin: 2em 0;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      color: var(--light-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }
    
    /* 响应式设计 */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .header {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 0 1rem 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p>动态路由文档</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <%- content %>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>由 FeedHub 动态路由系统提供 | 路径: <%= routePath %></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>